address: Jl. Mayor Metra No.14, Paket Agung, Kec. Buleleng, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81117, Indonesia
review 1: comfortable place to relax, good photo spot, and also a very affordable menu
review 2:
The fact that this coffeeshop owner care to spend some time to educate you about coffee and brewing alone deserve a five-star rating. Complimented by a great taste in authentic coffee brewing, makes it even more worth it. Don't worry about the price though, as the coffee could easily worth double the price tag if not more.

If you are into something special, try their cold brew, a slowly dripped-with-ice product which takes about 10 hours to produce. It's a masterpiece. Will come back for more!!
review 3: Young vibe/atmosphere, a lot of choice of drinks. For me the lemonade was a bit too sweet. But friendly staff
review 4: Good Vibes, Good Food, Good Beverages.. Perfect!!
review 5: Cozy place to hangout with friends and have an authentic taste of coffee and food also.

name: Puri Kanginan Buleleng
address: V3GW+6WP, Jl. Gajah Mada, Kp. Singaraja, Kec. Buleleng, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81118, Indonesia
review 1: "Exceptional experience! This museum truly offers a profound journey into the history of Hinduism. With a rich collection of historical artifacts, every corner radiates spiritual elegance. Interactive exhibits and knowledgeable guides make each visit more meaningful. The atmosphere is tranquil, as if transporting us back to a past full of wisdom. Truly an inspiring destination, deserving of 5 stars!"
review 2: Puri Kanginan Buleleng is a historic royal heritage place on the island of Bali precisely in Buleleng regency, this place is very comfortable to visit and of course we get a lot of historical knowledge about the origin of Puri Kanginan Buleleng.
review 3: The only preserved castle in Buleleng, still complete, is the residence of his descendants
review 4: This puri is very beautiful and unique, it has its own characteristics, which made me interested in visiting here
review 5: The best place in Buleleng because it has memories of past historical times, the buildings are still sturdy
